# Holistic Reports — Series Index & Methodology

**Purpose.** A numbered series of end-to-end solver validation reports. Each
report runs the **same frozen payload** against the current solver image and
measures every accuracy / objective / analyzer surface. New reports are
written only after a batch of fixes has landed, so each report-pair
(`#N` → `#N+1`) is a concrete before/after diff.

